0.en: Current NordPool electricity price, tax/margin excluded, ¢/kWh

1.en: Price rank in 9 hours, sliding windows, 1 if now lowest price, 9 highest

2.en: Price rank in 24 hours, sliding window, 1 if now lowest price, 24 highest

3.en: Price rank in 24 hours, fixed nychthemeron 00:00-23:59, 1 if now lowest price, 24 if highest

4.en: Price rank in fixed 8 hour block

5.en: Average price in 9 hours sliding window, ¢/kWh

6.en: Average price in 24 hours sliding window, ¢/kWh

13.en: Price ratio % to sliding 9 hours average

14.en: Price ratio % to sliding 24 hours average

20.en: Solar power forecast for local panels, next 24 hours, kWh

21.en: Value of future solar power, next 24 h, €

22.en: average price of future solar power, next 24 h, ¢/kWh

23.en: Future average solar power price is higher than current price, ¢/kWh

100.en: True if there is extra production, measured from grid or inverter production or estimated from solar forecast. See current source from variable 700.

101.en: Average production during this period, measured W

102.en: Average power exported to the grid during this period, measured W

103.en: Energy exported to the grid during this period, measured Wh

104.en: Energy exported to the grid now, measured W

111.en: Current month and day, e.g. 501 first of May

116.en: Current hour and minute, e.g. 1200 - noon

130.en: True if day tariff (Finnish tariff, 0700-2200) effective.

140.en: True if winter day tariff (Finnish) effective

160.en: Estimated (load*uptime) total consumption of channels during this period, Wh

401.en: Solar forecast based counter for load profile. Counts from 0 to M during this period, where M = (60*day forecasted solar/period forecasted solar).

402.en: Estimated solar production during this period so far, based on local solar forecast, Wh.

411.en: Average wind power in Finland tomorrow (d+1), MW

412.en: Average wind power in Finland the day after tomorrow (d+2) MW

421.en: Average wind power in Finland in the same 8 h block tomorrow (d+1) MW

422.en: Average wind power in Finland in the same 8 h block the day after tomorrow (d+2) MW

430.en: Solar volume rank of current period within day (24 h) based on solar forecast.

701.en: Netting info source, 0) no estimate, 1) grid measurement (103) 2) production MEASUREMENT (105) - (estimated channel consumption (160) + baseload)  3) production FORECAST (402) - (estimated channel consumption (160) + baseload)
